# Agent Dashboard KPI Definitions

1. Average Handling Time (AHT)
2. After Call Work (ACW)
3. Calls per Hour
4. Total Number of Calls Offered
5. Total Number of Calls Answered
6. Occupancy Rate (Percentage of time agents spent handling customer interactions versus waiting for calls)
7. Transfers (Number of calls transferred to other agents or departments)
8. Shrinkage (Time lost due to non-productive activities)
9. Absenteeism (Tracking unplanned leaves and adherence to schedules)
10. Consultant Score
